name: Tomb of Nekhen
description:
The Tomb of Nekhen is the oldest
discovered tomb with painted
decorations. It is believed the
tomb dates back to the end of
prehistoric Egypt, around
3200–3100 BC. Are we going to
discover new civilizations in the
future, when we explore other
planets to find life? A human being
simply can not help himself
wondering and idealizing this
moment when we finally do. 1440
x 1440 px
